# Normalize line endings to LF in the repo (checkout native), so generated
# mirrors and source files stay byte-identical across macOS/Linux/Windows —
# the same cross-platform discipline the product enforces.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Lockfiles and snapshots: keep LF, never treat as text needing CRLF.
package-lock.json -text

# Binaries (none yet, but future-proof).
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.ico binary
